<body class="landing-page">
<nav class="navbar navbar-transparent navbar-absolute">
  <div>
    <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
    <div class="navbar-header">
      <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navigation-example">
        <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
      </button>
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="">
        <%= image_tag("img/logo.png", position: "fixed" ,float: "none" ,width: "150", height: "150", alt: "handnhand2") %>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navigation-example">
      <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-static-top">
        <li>
        <a href="#top">
          About
        </a>
      </li>
        <li>
        <a href="#mid">
          Categories
        </a>
      </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#contact">
            Contact
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="header header-filter" style="background: url('http://i.huffpost.com/gen/2746982/images/o-STUDENTS-VOLUNTEERING-facebook.jpg');">
  <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h1 class="title">Hand-n-Hand Volunteering</h1>

          <h4>We have the cause. You have the effect.  Find an opportunity that's right for you!</h4>
          <br />
          <br />
          <br />
          <br />
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ" class="btn btn-danger btn-raised btn-lg">
            <i class="fa fa-play"></i> Join Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="main main-raised">
    <div class="container" id="top">
      <div class="section text-center section-landing">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
            <h2 class="title">Bringing Students and Community Together!</h2>
            <!-- the class="description" is what makes the font light -->
            <h5 class="description">Hand-n-Hand Volunteering is a non-commercial volunteering website created by two graduating students (Spencer Torrico and Joey Hawilah) at ASU Polytechnic.  The goal of this website is to help students, both new and continuing, find volunteering opportunities in the local area for the purpose of helping their community, getting the change to meet other students and members of the community, and obtaining critical volunteer time to satisfy scholarship requirements.
            </h5>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="info">
                <h4 class="info-title">By Students, For Students</h4>
                <p>While this site is for non-commercial use and not ASU affiliated, we are proud to say that all the work that went into this project was done using the knowledge obtained during our time at ASU.  Our hope is this will exemplify the coursework ASU can provide for future students!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="info">
                <h4 class="info-title">Second Feature</h4>
                <p>Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="info">
                <h4 class="info-title">Third Feature</h4>
                <p>Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section text-center" id="mid">
        <h2 class="title">Volunteer Categories</h2>

        <div class="team">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="team-player">
                <%= image_tag("img/dog.jpg", class: "img-raised img-circle")%>
                <h4 class="title">Animals <br />
                </h4>
                <p class="description">Perfect for the animal lover!  You can find local shelters that need help by clicking <%= link_to 'HERE', animal_path %>.  You're already on your way to improving the life of a shelter pet!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="team-player">
                <%= image_tag("img/community.jpg", class: "img-raised img-circle")%>
                <h4 class="title">Community<br />
                </h4>
                <p class="description">Being active in  your community is as fun as it is rewarding.  Got some free time and not sure what to do?  Click <a href="#">HERE</a> and see what volunteer opportunities are awaiting you in your local area!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="team-player">
                <%= image_tag("img/school.jpg", class: "img-raised img-circle")%>
                <h4 class="title">Schools<br />
                </h4>
                <p class="description">If investing in helping kids succeed is your main goal, you're in the right place.  With the time you give, you offer students a supportive environment that will help them grow and learn!  So click <%= link_to 'HERE', school_path %> and help brighten a students future today!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>


      <div class="section landing-section" id="contact">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
            <h2 class="text-center title">Contact</h2>
            <h4 class="text-center description">Have a question? Or maybe you just want to say hi; either way, lets chat!</h4>
            <form class="contact-form">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-group label-floating">
                    <label class="control-label">My name is</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-group label-floating">
                    <label class="control-label">My email is</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-group label-floating">
                <label class="control-label">And this is my message to you</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" rows="4"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 text-center">
                  <button class="btn btn-primary btn-raised">
                    Send Message
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="pull-left">
        <ul>

        </ul>
      </nav>
      <div class="copyright pull-right">
        &copy; 2017, All images taken from Google Images
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>

<%= render 'script' %>


